g with the by-laws and procedures?</span></p></div><div class="c17"><p class="c18"><a href="#cmnt_ref16" id="cmnt16">[p]</a><span class="c5 c15">Actually I think it is necessary to see a treasurers report at every board meeting.</span></p></div><div class="c17"><p class="c18"><a href="#cmnt_ref17" id="cmnt17">[q]</a><span class="c5 c15">I think the members should have a way to oust / replace the board also.</span></p></div><div class="c17"><p class="c18"><a href="#cmnt_ref18" id="cmnt18">[r]</a><span class="c5 c15">Really?</span></p></div></body></html>